paragraph-sm.text: The UC Conservation Genomics Consortium’s ongoing project, funded by the UC Catalyst Grant Program, is aiming to establish a genomics network across six UC campuses in order to support research, develop new analytical tools, host workshops, and more. The Consortium has created a website to keep track of the project, click on the link to find out more.
